<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.1">
<l>nāvakāriyañ collilātavar nāḷtoṟumvirun tōmpuvār</l>
<l>tēvakāriyañ ceytuvētampa yiṉṟuvāḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>mūvarkāriya muntiruttummu talvaṉaiccinti yātavap</l>
<l>pāvakārika ḷaippaṭaittava ṉeṅṅaṉampaṭait tāṉkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr dwell those whose tongues</l>
<l rend="indent">never speak of evil acts [and]</l>
<l>those who maintian the feast each day,</l>
<l rend="indent">repeating the Vedas and performing virtuous deeds.</l>
<l>Why did the Creator create those sinners</l>
<l rend="indent">who do not think of the First Cause Lord,</l>
<l>who rectifies the deeds of the three?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
